DYNAGNN uses the following third-party software. This file lists **direct** Python dependencies from `requirements.txt`, plus PyTorch (installed separately before `requirements.txt`; see README). Transitive dependencies installed by `pip` are not listed individually; regenerate a full report with:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install pip-licenses
pip-licenses --from=requirements.txt --format=markdown --with-urls --with-license-file
